snippet: The Jamaican sprinter Yohan Blake experienced a setback in his return from injury, pulling up during the 100 meters at the Glasgow Grand Prix, falling to the track and leaving in a wheelchair.
lead_paragraph: The Jamaican sprinter Yohan Blake experienced a setback in his return from injury, pulling up during the 100 meters at the Glasgow Grand Prix, falling to the track and leaving in a wheelchair.

headline.print_headline: Fresh Blake injury fears after pulling up in race
